snippet.title: INCISION - Transitory Termination Update
snippet.description:
INCISION is growing and getting even bloodier! Watch the trailer for the highly anticipated new update, which will be available on June 4th.

This meaty update adds a  whole new map, and two devilish bosses to deal with. Do you have what it takes to take them down?


-------------------------------------------------
INCISION is all old-school FPS action. No Bullshit. Lots of blood & gore. Slaughter your way through nightmarish industrial mazes, transformed cityscapes, and surreal alien structures to cut down the Growth in this ultraviolent, fast-paced, and merciless retro-styled first-person shooter.

GET INCISION NOW ON STEAM
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1734680/INCISION/
